snippet.title: Best VGM 2184 - Mii Channel
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 1886 - https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RBKbYPqJNOw

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Wii
Mii Channel (2006)
Kazumi Totaka
Super Smash Bros. Brawl version arranged by Shogo Sakai
